==============================================================
  Content
==============================================================

1 .. Create images for the document
2 .. Compile the document
3 .. Clean after compilation

--------------------------------------------------------------
1 Create images for the document
--------------------------------------------------------------

a) Create .eps files
b) Open a terminal and rationalize the .eps files with
   eps2eps FILE.eps

--------------------------------------------------------------
2 Compile the document
--------------------------------------------------------------

a) Open a terminal
b) Use the makefile
	 make tex	-> create .dvi file
	 make dvi	-> create .ps file
	 make pdf	-> create .pdf file
	 make all	-> everything above
	 make PDF	-> view PDF file

--------------------------------------------------------------
3 Clean after compilation
--------------------------------------------------------------

a) Open a terminal
b) Install latexmk
   e.g. sudo apt-get install latexmk
c) Use the makefile
   make clean
